name: Quotes
tagline: Read some of my favourite Quotes below.
body:
* > Things may come to those who _wait_, but only the **things** left by those who _Hustle._ ![Hustle_Quotes](http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sOACc9LHlzk/URNNBnBMFII/AAAAAAAAAyo/tmO4G1Lcx3g/s1600/hustle.png) * > _Failure_ is simply an _opportunity_ to begin again, this time more _Intelligently._ ![Opportunity_Quote](http://img.picturequotes.com/2/14/13943/failure-is-simply-the-opportunity-to-begin-again-this-time-more-intelligently-quote-3.jpg) * > Everything is OKAY in the END like a _movie_, if it's not OKAY then it's not the END. ![Okay_Ending_Quote](https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/236x/a3/da/8a/a3da8ace0456f11cd1d3213604456f22.jpg) * > Do not pray for an _Easy life_, pray for the **strength** to endure a _Difficult one._ ![Strength_Quote](http://www.mymotivationclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Screen-Shot-2015-01-09-at-8.06.09-PM.png) * > If your plan doesn't work out exactly as you Hoped, _learn_ from what went wrong and _try_ again. * > Whether you think **YOU can**, or think you can't **You are always Right.** ![YOU_Can_Quote](https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Co4Fb2iZ7uCijSUFUit5sPV-YxbJiob3X2mSUYxBaJDFHsItZ0E74RrITfpCsWqSqa6g8m82Eg2Ag9qlVPC5r8lOvaMpB5EXQFL-tmfwI8hJYF0anhnvVFBmCHDB2o9Bdg) * > To get over one _addiction_, you have to become _addicted to something else_. * > **DO** or **DO NOT**. There is **NO TRY**. ![NO_Try_Quote](https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6wyG4iInKPA/maxresdefault.jpg) *** Thanks for Showing Interest. Best is yet to come.
